Package net.sourceforge.waters.model.des

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AutomatonProxy
    A finite-state machine.
    ConflictCounterExampleProxy
    A counterexample that shows that a model is blocking or has a deadlock.
    CounterExampleProxy
    A counterexample to show that a model fails to satisfy some property.
    DualCounterExampleProxy
    A counterexample consisting of two traces.
    EventProxy
    An event used by the automata in a DES.
    LoopCounterExampleProxy
    A counterexample that shows that a model fails a liveness property.
    ProductDESProxy
    A collection of finite-state machines.
    ProductDESProxyFactory  
    ProductDESProxyVisitor  
    SafetyCounterExampleProxy
    A counterexample that shows that a model fails a safety property.
    StateProxy
    A state of an automaton.
    TraceProxy
    A execution sequence for some automata of a product DES.
    TraceStepProxy
    A step in a trace.
    TransitionProxy
    A transition of an automaton.

    A GNU Trove hashing strategy for transitions in nondeterministic automata.

    ProductDESHashCodeVisitor
